enhanced_by.reason: The method managedSubDetails fetches asset details for a managed sub-account, which can be used to set up the initial state before invoking managedSubAccountSnapshot.
Depositing assets into the managed sub-account can affect the snapshot, so it should be invoked before taking the snapshot.
The method managedSubDetails can be used to verify the asset details after the snapshot, ensuring that the snapshot accurately reflects the current state of the managed sub-account.
Withdrawing assets from the managed sub-account can be used to verify that the snapshot correctly captures the state before and after the withdrawal.
